value.title: Principles Of Excellence Program | Veterans Affairs
value.twitter_cards_description: Learn about guidelines for programs that receive federal funding through programs like the GI Bill. Some foreign schools, high schools, internships, residencies, and apprenticeships don't have to follow these guidelines.
